进入容器内部：

docker run -d `
  --name mysql8 `
  -p 3306:3306 `
  -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=123456 `
  -v D:\docker\mysql\data:/var/lib/mysql `
  --character-set-server=utf8mb4 `
  --collation-server=utf8mb4_unicode_ci `
  --restart always `
  mysql:8

执行修改命令：

 docker exec -it mysql8 mysql -uroot -p123456
ALTER USER 'root'@'%' IDENTIFIED WITH mysql_native_password BY '123456';
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;
EXIT;

1. JDBC URL (Java/Spring Boot):

jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/your_database?useSSL=false&allowPublicKeyRetrieval=true&serverTimezone=UTC



